name: dentsu x AWS Industry Week - Cheers2Web3

metadata.name: Cheers2Web3 #1
metadata.description:
感謝參與dentsu x AWS Industry Week - Web3與元宇宙議程，憑此NFT和您的名片，到現場dentsu櫃台兌換啤酒，10/26活動限定喔！

dentsu Web3有區塊鏈專家「寶博士」葛如鈞與行銷團隊為企業提供顧問諮詢、行銷活動策畫、NFT發行管理、Web3會員經營等服務，並和LeadBest顧問集團旗下「EchoX虛實共鳴科技」啟動技術合作。想要了解更多請聯繫min.w@dentsu.com。

Thank you for attending dentsu x AWS Industry Week - Web3 & the Metaverse. With this NFT and your business card, you get exclusive access to our beer which is only available at our stand on 10/26!

dentsu Web3 Consulting provides clients with services and solutions including: consulting, planning, NFT management, Web3 CRM, along with blockchain expert Dr. Ju-Chun Ko, and our tech partner EchoX under LeadBest Consulting Group. For more information please contact our us at: min.w@dentsu.com.
